{"tid":398491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過搭地鐵塞得太入搞到落唔到車？","createTime":"2017-09-13T08:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T10:23:48.000Z","uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a049906168880b63ef9c6cd39237077627183df","tid":398491,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"要死死氣下個站落車搭返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14367b4c42653926a23417d2c9355f75676db6a4","tid":398491,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"格硬沖出去"},{"pid":"4d96edf4ba20d969952666d7cd7c528bb34eabd0","tid":398491,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"中學時試過俾兩個「朋友」㩒住唔畀我落車"},{"pid":"5d8728c0a75d586bc072c32cf771a70b7b990590","tid":398491,"uid":15639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"出曬聲 講曬唔該 借一借 <br />\n唔讓就爆出去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99af43060dfec5f4f5ea6394a51e10279897803b","tid":398491,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"講哂唔該借借都無人郁<br />\n最後夾硬撞出去<br />\n然後上車有條仆街專登戟鳩我<br />\n好撚無品"},{"pid":"58c5e7abdf624ec1811d962a1859c0a4fbbe0aea","tid":398491,"uid":17089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"出落後上啊！"},{"pid":"79cb057a7c46ad910566f18e5f274c7fa62bd027","tid":398491,"uid":17089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先落後上啊！</blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe667d1b660d07e3266ef72f49dea029c6bf6af","tid":398491,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先落後上啊！</blockquote><br />\n好撚多人唔理, 尤其呀叔呀嬸"},{"pid":"c0931a34c607d2d4c1a5301feaebd00be88e57a0","tid":398491,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出曬聲 講曬唔該 借一借 <br />\n唔讓就爆出去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭輕鐵一定要咁做啦 有時企門口，但上車啲人湧入嚟都出唔到去<br />\n<br />\n爆到啲廢老燥就啱"},{"pid":"b395857b7b9f59bd2e514c9f76cf650f32570652","tid":398491,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"大叫一聲 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n挺胸收腹，行正中間，擘大對閪冧眼望撚實啲想沖入嚟嘅撚屌<br />\n再拎個膊頭輕輕撞一撞啲入到一半俾你嚇呆咗嘅嘅仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7d7b25d95d266697f7af498f16274d37d2c1f6","tid":398491,"uid":101367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰陣仲讀緊中學搭地鐵去太子補習 本身以為太子好多人都會出咪行入啲囉 點知到咗站無人出不特止啲人仲逼入黎 之後我勁大聲講唔該讓讓都無人理 之後我遮住個校徽撞開啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d2346ab116455c19b39cee1abcaca3498d2f32","tid":398491,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:08:20.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間最難落車車站<br />\n東涌綫往香港，南昌站冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102922c96ee7f3579a7123a49f93bc56e089e7ce","tid":398491,"uid":112709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"一鳩野撞撚開曬啲廢中廢老"}]}